# map-ui-lib Rules

- Never import `maplibre-gl` or `react-map-gl` in library code.
- Keep domain state controlled via props and callbacks.
- Use `mapui:` Tailwind utilities in library components.
- Prefer existing hooks (`useOgcCollections`, `useOgcFeatures`) for OGC data access.
- Export new APIs from local index files and package entry points.

Required references:

- `.claude/skills/project-conventions/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/add-map-component/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/add-ogc-hook/SKILL.md`
